Test Case 1 – Login and Logout

Test Objective:
Verify that a registered user can successfully log in and log out.

Test Steps:

    1. Launch the browser and open https://automationexercise.com/

    2. Click on “Signup / Login” link in the top menu.

    3. Enter a valid email and password in the login section.

    4. Click on Login button.

    5. Verify that “Logged in as [username]” is displayed.

    6. Click on Logout from the top menu.

    7. Verify that the login page is displayed again.

Expected Result:
User should be able to log in successfully and log out without any error.